        <mxCell id="ZR-NAflUI1GGsINpZlQH-31" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#A20025,#601414);strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);movable=1;resizable=1;rotatable=1;deletable=1;editable=1;locked=0;connectable=1;strokeWidth=3;align=center;fontColor=default;fontSize=30;" value="Critérios de Aceitação" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="310" width="280" x="210" y="390" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ZR-NAflUI1GGsINpZlQH-32" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#A20025,#FFFFFF);strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);strokeWidth=3;fontColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=25;" value="&lt;blockquote style=&quot;margin: 0 0 0 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;1,6,0,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;1,6,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;1,6,1,0&quot;&gt;Alta (Obrigatório por lei)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="1260" x="491" y="-180" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ZR-NAflUI1GGsINpZlQH-33" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#A20025,#FFFFFF);strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);strokeWidth=3;fontColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=25;" value="&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;1,7,0,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;1,7,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,7,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;1. O utilizador encontra-se autenticado com o perfil de topo na hierarquia financeira (Administração,&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Tesouraria ou Contabilista).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,7,1,2&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;2. O sistema possui os dados fiscais do clube devidamente configurados (NIF, morada sede, série de&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;faturação).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,7,1,4&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;3. Existem recibos ou faturas emitidos e validados no período a exportar.&lt;/p&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="260" width="1261" x="490" y="-120" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ZR-NAflUI1GGsINpZlQH-34" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#A20025,#FFFFFF);strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);strokeWidth=3;fontColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=25;" value="&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;1,8,0,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;1,8,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,8,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;1. O sistema compila as transações do período selecionado e gera um ficheiro informático (tipicamente em&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;formato XML) que respeita a estrutura imposta pelas Finanças.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,8,1,2&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;2. O ficheiro fica disponível para &lt;i data-path-to-node=&quot;1,8,1,2&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;35&quot;&gt;download&lt;/i&gt; seguro na máquina do utilizador para posterior submissão oficial.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,8,1,4&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;3. É criado um registo de auditoria interno documentando a data, a hora e o utilizador que realizou a&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;extração dos dados.&lt;/p&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="250" width="1260" x="490" y="140" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ZR-NAflUI1GGsINpZlQH-35" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#A20025,#FFFFFF);strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);strokeWidth=3;fontColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=25;" value="&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;1,9,0,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;1,9,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,9,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;1. A interface de exportação deve permitir a seleção precisa do intervalo temporal (ex: mês civil ou ano&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;fiscal completo).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,9,1,2&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;2. O sistema deve efetuar uma validação prévia dos dados e emitir um relatório de erros caso detete&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;faturas ou recibos com anomalias (ex: documentos sem associação de taxa de IVA correta).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,9,1,4&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;3. O acesso a esta funcionalidade de exportação de dados em massa tem de ser rigorosamente barrado a&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;qualquer outro tipo de perfil de utilizador.&lt;/p&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="310" width="1260" x="490.5" y="390" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
  </diagram>
